title: I cannot open some pictures or video clips. Why?
answer:
Possible causes are as follows:


	  The mobile phone does not support the file format.


	  The mobile phone's RAM is insufficient.


	  The file has corrupted.


	  The file is copyright-protected.


	  The mobile phone's battery level low.

      Unknown errors occurred in the mobile phone's OS or applications. Restart the mobile phone and try again.
